channel.title: WildyCrash - OS/PK SPAWN - Can you Survive it?
channel.description:
Hello Guys,
WildyCrash.com
A new awesome OS Server has born (WildyCrash), We've a team of developers who're daily doing updates on bases what YOU want!
WildyCrash.com
It's online for 1 day and we've already reached around 30 online. Like I said earlier it's really new so we're still looking for staff our moderators Server Supporters and Administrators, owner and developer spots are currently full. It is a Old school Pk/spawn server with awesome combat and lots of features.
WildyCrash.com
This is our Official Promo Video,
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6t3ErXaotMg
WildyCrash is a server designed to give you, the players, the best experience we can offer. With a team of the most elite and experienced developers and staff, we are capable of making your 317 server dreams come to life. Always keeping it fun, professional, and efficient, the staff team is here to create a server worth playing and an uplifting community for the players to thrive in. Taking every suggestion into consideration, we want to hear from you to improve the game according to your standards. With new content, an elite staff team, and an amazing community, we welcome you to join us over at WildyCrash.
I had some issues with my computer so I couldn't take pictures if you want to see some pics look us up in toplists like runelocus.
